      <body>
         <div type="writingSession" n="1"><p><pb facs="1893-06-09_AS_RBH_1"/><salute>Lieber Richard,</salute> ich ko<c rendition="#gemination-m">mm</c>e <anchor type="commentary" xml:id="K_L00219-2"/>morgen<note type="commentary" corresp="K_L00219-2"><ref type="schnitzler-tagebuch" subtype="See" target="1893-06-09"/>.</note> um
                  <time>6 Uhr</time> mit Vergnügen. <anchor type="commentary" xml:id="K_L00219-1"/><date>So<c rendition="#gemination-n">nn</c>tag</date><note type="commentary" corresp="K_L00219-1"><ref type="schnitzler-tagebuch" subtype="See" target="1893-06-11"/>.
                  </note>
               handelts sichs hoffentlich endlich um Sie? –</p><closer>Herzlich Ihr<lb/><signed>Arthur</signed></closer><postscript><dateline rend="right"><date>8/6 93</date></dateline></postscript></div>
      </body>
